    Defines a class for maintaining an array of School objects
    Version:
    2018.11.16 KNOWN BUGS: 1. There is no limiting the weights in the [1..5] range. 2. No other bug. Likely I did not test hard enough. FEATURE:-) It uses its own selection sorting method, and this can be slow for large collections of Schools. Better to have flexibility.
    Author:
    Takis Metaxas, based on previous assignment solutions
